 |quote = 借玉通灵存翰墨，为芹辛苦见平生。
 |source = 周汝昌，自叙对联，《周汝昌校订批点本石头记》。<ref name="bear"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://roll.sohu.com/20120601/n344596932.shtml |title=为芹辛苦见平生 |date=2012-06-01 |accessdate=2012-06-01 |work=搜狐 |archive-date=2020-07-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200704124329/http://roll.sohu.com/20120601/n344596932.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>
